caption: @beaub  I know you probably won't see this but I just wanted to let you know how much I love you ❤️ even though I've never met you or spoken to you, it always feels like you're there for me if something goes wrong at school because I can just come home and watch you on YouTube and it makes me feel 1,000,000x better. You (and the other janoskians) have given me the confidence to stand up to all the bullies and helped me with my depression ALOT! I really hope that I can meet you one day and my little brother wants to as well! I'm hopefully coming to Another Fail Tour! Also, thank you for following me on here and Instagram; it means so much to me❤️
